    "The prompt for this approach is shown as 'Base+Adjust' in Table II.The gpt-4o-mini LLM sometimes struggled with the 'Base+Adjust' approach and would greatly adjust negative reviews upward when it didn't make sense to do so.",
    "For example, for the target score of 0.10, the word \"Undesirable\", and the review \"I found my experience with the product to be quite disappointing.",
    "It didn't meet my expectations, and many features seemed lacking or ineffective.",
    "Overall, it left me feeling frustrated rather than satisfied.\"",
